Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by MISSING
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by MISSING to Request Payment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time for Declaration REJECTED by MISSING to be followed by Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by MISSING
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by MISSING
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by MISSING to Payment Handled
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by MISSING to Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Time until Declaration REJECTED by MISSING after Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Time from Declaration REJECTED by MISSING to the next Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE

Name: Minimum time it takes Declaration REJECTED by MISSING after Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time for Declaration REJECTED by MISSING cycle from submission to payment handling
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for Declaration REJECTED by MISSING to be resolved before Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Time of Declaration REJECTED by MISSING cycle from initial submission to final approval or rejection
